name: GhostAttack.Cat
description:
This NFT is the first of “Spooky Artemizia” collection, which consists of three arts, each one different and unique.
The lil artemizia decided to visit a cemetery  with a bouquet flowers on the hand on the day of the dead on the night to pay tribute to her deads, when with fast step an evil ghost crossed on her way, the poor Artemizia suffer a fright that his heart almost came out of his chest.
